dc_title_s: Land Use Vilas County, WI YE2016
dc_description_s: This polygon data layer represents land use for Vilas County, Wisconsin at year-end 2016. It is a feature class within the geodatabase Vilas_LandUse_YE2016.gdb.
uw_supplemental_s: For complete metadata documentation, please visit https://maps.vilascountywi.gov/data.htmlThis data was submitted to the UW geospatial archive in 2017. Content may be considered current as of December 31, 2016. It was published to the UW geospatial archive as part of the Wisconsin Department of Administration Land Information Program annual collection of public data for the year 2017.
